remium/israels-top-court-steps-in-to-stop-state-sending-palestinian-cancer-patients-back-to-gaza/0000018e-5e32-d27e-a7af-7efe67c40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在约旦河西岸发动两次空袭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-air-strike-on-four-terrorists-in-jenin-including-two-top-islamic-jihad-operatives/0000018e-5e2a-d27e-a7af-7eee3ff30000</link><description>艾哈迈德·巴拉卡特是以色列在杰宁和努尔沙姆斯难民营空袭中丧生的人之一，以色列国防军称他去年对赫尔梅什实施了枪击袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 23:27:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-air-strike-on-four-terrorists-in-jenin-including-two-top-islamic-jihad-operatives/0000018e-5e2a-d27e-a7af-7eee3ff30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院史无前例地允许拆除非致命袭击恐怖分子的家庭住宅</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-okays-demolition-of-family-home-of-terrorist-behind-non-fatal-attack/0000018e-5db5-d4b2-afcf-dfb728ec0000</link><description>当场被杀的 Khaled Al-Mohtaseb 的家人就拆除令向法院请愿，称他们没有参与导致一名边境警察受重伤的袭击事件</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 23:17:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-okays-demolition-of-family-home-of-terrorist-behind-non-fatal-attack/0000018e-5db5-d4b2-afcf-dfb728ec0000</guid></item><item><title>数十名美国前高级官员敦促拜登：如果以色列阻止加沙援助，请考虑限制美国对以色列的援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/former-officials-urge-biden-mull-restricting-assistance-to-israel-if-it-blocks-gaza-aid/0000018e-5e0f-d4b2-afcf-de9f4cf60000</link><description>近70名美国前国家安全高级官员和外交官敦促美国总统采取更有力的措施，促进人道主义准入和保护加沙平民</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/former-officials-urge-biden-mull-restricting-assistance-to-israel-if-it-blocks-gaza-aid/0000018e-5e0f-d4b2-afcf-de9f4cf60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正在成为“贱民国家”吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/is-israel-becoming-a-pariah-state/0000018e-4d66-dfb8-adef-dd76d4820000</link><description>在《国土报》-加州大学洛杉矶分校会议上，阿隆·平卡斯、艾哈迈德·马赫、雅埃尔·杰尔曼和尼姆罗德·戈伦讨论了以色列外交关系危机的严重程度以及是否可以解决这一问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 22:43:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/is-israel-becoming-a-pariah-state/0000018e-4d66-dfb8-adef-dd76d4820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长在以色列奖问题上再次搞砸、出尔反尔、辩称无罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-education-minister-screws-up-backtracks-pleads-innocent-on-israel-prize/0000018e-5d63-d27e-a7af-7fef83f20000</link><description>教育部长约阿夫·基什(Yoav Kisch)在得知内塔尼亚胡批评者赢得了创业奖后，取消了今年的以色列奖奖项类别，引发了一场风暴，但现在必须亲自将奖项交给他</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 20:16:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-education-minister-screws-up-backtracks-pleads-innocent-on-israel-prize/0000018e-5d63-d27e-a7af-7fef83f20000</guid></item><item><title>托尼·库什纳：以色列加沙战争“在我看来很像种族清洗”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-20/ty-article-podcast/tony-kushner-israels-gaza-war-looks-a-lot-like-ethnic-cleansing-to-me/0000018e-5cbb-d3c4-a7cf-7dffbba50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 19:53:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-20/ty-article-podcast/tony-kushner-israels-gaza-war-looks-a-lot-like-ethnic-cleansing-to-me/0000018e-5cbb-d3c4-a7cf-7dffbba50000</guid></item><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡领导下的以色列，加沙战争正在摧毁仅存的民主价值观</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/in-netanyahus-israel-the-gaza-war-is-wrecking-what-remains-of-democratic-values/0000018e-5cdd-d411-a3df-dcdfbad90000</link><description>以色列历史上最右翼的政府从未放弃与自由民主的斗争。战争是接管的好时机</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 19:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/in-netanyahus-israel-the-gaza-war-is-wrecking-what-remains-of-democratic-values/0000018e-5cdd-d411-a3df-dcdfbad90000</guid></item><item><title>纽约一家犹太咖啡馆店面喷有反以色列、亲巴勒斯坦的涂鸦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/anti-israel-pro-palestinian-graffiti-sprayed-ona-new-york-jewish-cafe-storefront/0000018e-5cd1-d312-a7df-defbb3bd0000</link><description>邻居和顾客（其中一些人还披着以色列国旗）联合起来进行清理工作，他们聚集在咖啡馆前，对人行道进行高压清洗。纽约民主党众议员杰里·纳德勒表示，这次袭击是“一种懦弱的反犹太主义行为，我们的社区不能也不会容忍”</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/anti-israel-pro-palestinian-graffiti-sprayed-ona-new-york-jewish-cafe-storefront/0000018e-5cd1-d312-a7df-defbb3bd0000</guid></item><item><title>查克·舒默代表美国犹太人说话吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-20/ty-article/.highlight/does-chuck-schumer-speak-for-american-jews/0000018e-5ca0-d3c4-a7cf-7df4f43d0000</link><description>在发表具有里程碑意义的以色列演讲后，参议院多数党领袖试图平息对犹太建制组织最重要的保护伞团体的担忧。其领导层对他的言论继续表示震惊，而几个成员团体也表达了对舒默的支持</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:41:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-20/ty-article/.highlight/does-chuck-schumer-speak-for-american-jews/0000018e-5ca0-d3c4-a7cf-7df4f43d0000</guid></item><item><title>第 166 天你需要知道的是：内塔尼亚胡表示，准备拉法行动需要时间</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-166-hamas-claims-israel-rejected-cease-fire-proposal/0000018e-5cc0-d411-a3df-dcda44420001</link><description>就在内塔尼亚胡总理准备通过视频向参议院共和党人发表讲话的几个小时前，共和党官员表示，他们正在讨论邀请他在国会联席会议上发言 ■ 哈马斯高级官员表示，以色列对该组织停火提案的反应是否定的 ■ 准备出发内塔尼亚胡表示，在拉法的行动“需要一些时间” ■ 战争开始 166 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:28:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-166-hamas-claims-israel-rejected-cease-fire-proposal/0000018e-5cc0-d411-a3df-dcda44420001</guid></item><item><title>拜登政府在周日截止日期前暂停向以色列出售武器问题上存在分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-administration-split-on-suspending-arms-sales-to-israel-ahead-of-deadline-on-sunday/0000018e-5bea-d949-afae-5beeac6b0000</link><description>以色列远远没有兑现向加沙“大量提供援助”的承诺，使来自美国的武器流动陷入危险</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 16:04:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-administration-split-on-suspending-arms-sales-to-israel-ahead-of-deadline-on-sunday/0000018e-5bea-d949-afae-5beeac6b0000</guid></item><item><title>众议院共和党人考虑邀请内塔尼亚胡在国会联席会议上发表讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/house-republicans-mull-inviting-netanyahu-to-address-joint-session-of-congress/0000018e-5c55-df0b-a78f-ddffb9970000</link><description>这一邀请让人想起内塔尼亚胡2015年的讲话，该讲话旨在争取支持，反对奥巴马政府背后组织的伊朗核协议。此举发生之际，内塔尼亚胡对拜登政府批评以色列在加沙的行为感到明显愤怒</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 15:07:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/house-republicans-mull-inviting-netanyahu-to-address-joint-session-of-congress/0000018e-5c55-df0b-a78f-ddffb9970000</guid></item><item><title>死在以色列监狱的巴勒斯坦人的尸检显示医疗疏忽和瘀伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/autopsies-of-palestinians-who-died-in-israeli-prisons-indicate-medical-neglect-bruising/0000018e-56c6-dea2-a38e-57dfa5430000</link><description>上个月，以色列监狱服务设施中一名行政拘留者和一名安全囚犯死亡，据报道，监狱条件不断恶化，缺乏适当的医疗服务，部分原因是加沙战争爆发以来监狱严重过度拥挤。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:53:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-20/ty-article/.premium/autopsies-of-palestinians-who-died-in-israeli-prisons-indicate-medical-neglect-bruising/0000018e-56c6-dea2-a38e-57dfa5430000</guid></item><item>